name: Sky Cheese
description: Anxiety is here to make you think. Think for yourself, and for others around you. But if under stimulated anxiety will cause your mind to go hay wire. Though there are ways to help many choose to avoid medication. Art is often used to calm anxiety and light blue is the calming color they use most often for stress reduction. Gaze upon the beautiful moon and light baby blue skies and relax before you continue your day.
